{"id":"izhar","term":"Izhar","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Oil, one of the sons of Kohath, and grandson of Levi (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 6:18\">Ex. 6:18</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 6:21\">21</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 16:1\">Num. 16:1</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Exodus 6:18","Exodus 6:21","Numbers 16:1"]}